{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回 宴会。苏苏晕倒后醒来，发现自己身处一场奇迹般的宴会——宴席开在一片白玉山崖上。宴上四人：穿蓝衫的楚留香、独臂杀手、万福万寿园的金老太太、以及脸上有两个洞般深陷的神秘富豪。苏苏认出蓝衫人正是传说已死的楚留香，楚留香告诉她：有一个神秘组织正在查证他是否真死。更令苏苏震惊的是，那位面容沉静华贵的神秘富豪竟是楚留香最好的朋友胡铁花。胡铁花解释自己发财的原因：他以为楚留香已死，需要庞大财力来为挚友报仇。他坦承自己并非世人眼中的醉猫，而是刻意伪装——要对抗能杀死楚留香的那个庞大组织，需要朋友和金钱。独臂人始终沉默静坐。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你是不是楚留香？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真的就是那个楚留香？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "是的，我真的就是那个楚留香。我相信楚留香好像只有我一个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像他这种人如果太多，就不好玩了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个世界上如果没有像他这样的人，也不好玩了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "天下人都知道楚留香已经死了，如果你是楚留香，你怎么还没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我本来是要死的，而且已经决定要死了。只可惜我暂时还死不了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "因为你。最少有一部分原因是因为你，所以我才死不了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你死不了是因为我？还是你因为我而不想死了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我知道有一个人，一个非常神秘，非常有力量的人，组织了一个非常可怕的组织。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "这个组织唯一的目的，就是要查证我是不是已经死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "这件事当然是很不容易做到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的行踪在我十二三岁的时候就难查得到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一点我可以证明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "这个人是谁，其实你应该知道的，可是你又不敢相信。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "非但你不敢相信，天下江湖，恐怕也没有人敢相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我可以保证，天下江湖，谁也不会相信这个人就是胡铁花，更没有人会相信胡铁花会变成这么样一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你真的就是那个胡铁花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "好像是的。胡铁花好像也只有一个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你……你怎么会变成这样子的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我变成了什么样子？我现在的样子有什么奇怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "别的事我不知道，只有一件事我一定要问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "江湖中人都知道，胡铁花是个天生的穷鬼，可是现在你却好像有钱得要命。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "老婆要偷人，天要下雨，人要发财，都是没法子的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我本来是打死都不想发财的，可是那时候每个人都说楚留香已经死了，说得连我都不能不相信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "如果这个老臭虫真的死了，我怎么能不发财？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "老臭虫？难道你说楚香帅是个老臭虫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "他不是老臭虫谁是老臭虫？只不过除了我之外，叫他老臭虫的人好像并没有几个。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "老臭虫如果死了，你为什么一定要发财？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "因为老臭虫死了，我就要花钱，而且非花钱不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "因为报仇是件非常花钱的事。替别人报仇，也许只不过只要拼命就行了，可是要替楚留香报仇，就一定要花钱了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "你想想，这个老臭虫是个什么样的人？要什么样的人才能杀死他？要用什么法子才能杀死他？这其中要动员多少人？要有一个多精密的计划？最重要的一点是，杀了楚留香这么样一个人之后，要用多大的力量才能隐藏住这个秘密？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我不但不是别人想像中那么样的一个醉猫，而且比别人想像中要聪明十七八倍。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一点我当然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "要对付这样一个庞大的组织，当然绝不是一个人的力量所能做得到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就连我这样的天才，也做不到的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要对付这么样一个组织，最少要有三个条件。第一，是要有朋友，第二，是要有钱，第三，还是要有钱。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "朋友我一向是有的，而且都是好朋友，可是钱呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "所以你就一定要去赚钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "看样子，你好像也真的赚到了不少钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "岂止不少，而且很多。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你想赚钱的时候，就能赚到很多钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "看情况好像就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "赚钱真是这么容易的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "赚钱当然不是容易，如果有人说赚钱容易，那个人一定是乌龟。可是像我这样的天才，情况就不同了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我赚钱就是这样子的。有时候我想少赚一点都不行。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钱这种东西，就好像女人一样，你追她的时候，她板起脸不理你，你要推她的时候，推也推不了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这真是他的经验之谈，女人有时候真是这样子的，只不过一定要等活到我这么大年纪的时候才会承认。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "这不是我的经验之谈。这是老臭虫告诉我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    }
  ],
